name: Hectic (blueprint)
description:
IT'S BEEN CRAZY! It gave us opportunities but we have to cut the others and we can’t deny, it gave us pressure to always speaking even if we couldn’t but we can’t deny, it gave us a very bad sickness that we can’t deny, it gave us a bad behavior to leave the work and we can’t deny, it gave us something to hardly pull us up from everything, until our freedom become bias. We can’t run, no matter what it is, we have to face it, it has to happen. It’s been crazy! WE’VE BEEN CRAZY. 

Based on my experience in February 2022.

[Pictures are from Unsplash and Pexels]
